  "doc_id": "38474",
  "text": "Encyclopedia of Genes and Genomes (KEGG) pathway enrichment analysis. GO database was built by Gene Ontology Consortium, which described gene and their protein functions [CITATION_1] . Based on this database, screened DEGs in the two groups were functional annotated, and then significant GO terms were selected by Fisher exact test and multiple hypothesis test with the threshold of false discovery rate (FDR) <0.05. Beniamini-Hochberg (BH) method was utilized for correcting P-value to FDR [CITATION_2] .",
